<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Minecraft - Bergabung Sekarang!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background: url('https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1256974532397240342/1355196751031832767/image.png') no-repeat center center/cover;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .overlay {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff9800, #ff5722);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff9800, #ff5722);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff5722, #e64a19);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 28px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .social-links a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Acro Network</h1>
        <p>Bergabunglah dengan komunitas kami dan nikmati pengalaman bermain Minecraft yang seru dan menantang!</p>
        <p><strong>IP Server:</strong> play.acronetwork.my.id</p>
        <p><strong>Versi:</strong> 1.20+</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Gabung Sekarang!</a>
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>